27#pragma once
28
29#include "CacheStorageConnection.h"
30
31namespace WebCore {
32
33class WorkerGlobalScope;
34class WorkerLoaderProxy;
35
36class WorkerCacheStorageConnection final : public CacheStorageConnection {
37public:
38 static Ref<WorkerCacheStorageConnection> create(WorkerGlobalScope&);
39 ~WorkerCacheStorageConnection();
40
41 void clearPendingRequests();
42
43private:
44 explicit WorkerCacheStorageConnection(WorkerGlobalScope&);
45
46 // WebCore::CacheStorageConnection.
47 void open(const ClientOrigin&, const String& cacheName, DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierCallback&&) final;
48 void remove(uint64_t cacheIdentifier, DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierCallback&&) final;
49 void retrieveCaches(const ClientOrigin&, uint64_t updateCounter, DOMCacheEngine::CacheInfosCallback&&) final;
50
51 void retrieveRecords(uint64_t cacheIdentifier, const RetrieveRecordsOptions&, DOMCacheEngine::RecordsCallback&&) final;
52 void batchDeleteOperation(uint64_t cacheIdentifier, const ResourceRequest&, CacheQueryOptions&&, DOMCacheEngine::RecordIdentifiersCallback&&) final;
53 void batchPutOperation(uint64_t cacheIdentifier, Vector<DOMCacheEngine::Record>&&, DOMCacheEngine::RecordIdentifiersCallback&&) final;
54
55 void reference(uint64_t cacheIdentifier) final;
56 void dereference(uint64_t cacheIdentifier) final;
57
58 void doOpen(uint64_t requestIdentifier, const ClientOrigin&, const String& cacheName);
59 void doRemove(uint64_t requestIdentifier, uint64_t cacheIdentifier);
60 void doRetrieveCaches(uint64_t requestIdentifier, const ClientOrigin&, uint64_t updateCounter);
61 void doRetrieveRecords(uint64_t requestIdentifier, uint64_t cacheIdentifier, const URL&);
62 void doBatchDeleteOperation(uint64_t requestIdentifier, uint64_t cacheIdentifier, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, WebCore::CacheQueryOptions&&);
63 void doBatchPutOperation(uint64_t requestIdentifier, uint64_t cacheIdentifier, Vector<DOMCacheEngine::Record>&&);
64
65 void openOrRemoveCompleted(uint64_t requestIdentifier, const DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierOrError&);
66 void retrieveCachesCompleted(uint64_t requestIdentifier, DOMCacheEngine::CacheInfosOrError&&);
67 void retrieveRecordsCompleted(uint64_t requestIdentifier, DOMCacheEngine::RecordsOrError&&);
68 void deleteRecordsCompleted(uint64_t requestIdentifier, DOMCacheEngine::RecordIdentifiersOrError&&);
69 void putRecordsCompleted(uint64_t requestIdentifier, DOMCacheEngine::RecordIdentifiersOrError&&);
70
71 WorkerGlobalScope& m_scope;
72
73 RefPtr<CacheStorageConnection> m_mainThreadConnection;
74
75 HashMap<uint64_t, DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierCallback> m_openAndRemoveCachePendingRequests;
76 HashMap<uint64_t, DOMCacheEngine::CacheInfosCallback> m_retrieveCachesPendingRequests;
77 HashMap<uint64_t, DOMCacheEngine::RecordsCallback> m_retrieveRecordsPendingRequests;
78 HashMap<uint64_t, DOMCacheEngine::RecordIdentifiersCallback> m_batchDeleteAndPutPendingRequests;
79
80 uint64_t m_lastRequestIdentifier { 0 };
81};
82
83} // namespace WebCore
